Over the past six months, Takealot has given away gift vouchers to the value of R48,000 on the MyBroadband forum. The final giveaway launched this week, with R3,000 in vouchers up for grabs. To enter the competition, visit the page for Takealot’s Clearance Sale on its website, choose a product you would like to put a gift voucher towards, and post it in the competition thread on the MyBroadband forum. The rules and entry requirements are explained on the MyBroadband forum. Entrants stand a chance to win a R2,000 or R1,000 Takealot voucher. This week’s giveaway closes on 28 July 2017. This is the last giveaway in this series, so be sure to get your entries in to stand a chance to win.